properties.note:
Wyoming Territory (1868-07-25)

1868/07/25 -> 1890/07/09

The United States created Wyoming Territory with present boundaries from Dakota, Idaho, and Utah Territories.

(Trenholm, 1:83-84; U.S. Stat., vol. 15, ch. 235[1868], secs. 1, 17/pp. 178, 183; Van Zandt, 136, 144)
